{"tid":119214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死5隻]氣罐車撞遊神隊伍　打人肉保齡釀5死傷","createTime":"2017-02-13T14:49:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T14:49:54.000Z","uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7ed06441240cc1ff19ad74c6699079bebec3f53","tid":119214,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T14:49:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170213/bkncn-20170213192950765-0213_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170213%2Fbkncn-20170213192950765-0213_05011_001.html&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=7e913b55\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170213/bkncn-20170213192950765-0213_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170213/photo/bkncn-20170213192950765-0213_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170213%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170213192950765-0213_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=51ec4ea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣東潮州鐵汫線徑南村路段昨日發生一宗恐怖車禍，一輛氣罐車疑因煞車系統失靈，高速撞向遊神隊伍，輾過多人後衝入公路旁的草叢翻側。目擊者稱，事件釀成2死3傷，事發後現場傳出陣陣哭聲，地上遺下大量血漬。<br />\n<br />\n事發於下午2時許，肇事氣罐車從錢東往汫洲方向行駛，駛經徑南村路段時，遇上一隊巡遊隊伍，卻疑因煞車失靈，司機響按警告，但仍有部分站在公路旁的村民閃避不及，有人當場氣罐車輾過，更有人被捲入車底拖行。<br />\n<br />\n知情者透露，當時徑南村正舉行「營老爺」的祭祀活動，巡遊隊伍在公路旁敲鑼打鼓，不少村民在旁圍觀拍照，未料卻遭遇飛來橫禍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}